OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772143504
OL,3,CAssisted dying delays are 'reflections
OL,4,Cof good government' UK tells Isle of
OL,5,CMan
OL,7,FThe UK's Justice Minister has said
OL,8,Fdelays to the Isle of Man's assisted
OL,9,Fdying bill are a reflection of "good
OL,10,Fgovernment and international
OL,11,Fobligations".
OL,13,FThe island's Tynwald became the first
OL,14,Fparliament in the British Isles to
OL,15,Fagree a framework for assisted dying
OL,16,Fin March 2025, but the UK Ministry of
OL,17,FJustice still has not processed the
OL,18,Flegislation for royal assent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
